{"tid":1482234,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"而家 帶備 full gear 出發去維園  泳鏡， 口罩， 長遮， 頭盔， 黑衫","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:25:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5cfa209afc370f0314a70770380409357c8c4e0e","tid":1482234,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:49.000Z","msg":"而家 帶備 full gear 出發去維園<br />\n<br />\n泳鏡， 口罩， 長遮， 頭盔， 黑衫"},{"pid":"6f42b9d7e30d200730fee764e4d26da14d08c583","tid":1482234,"uid":139409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPC%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=c9e254ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPC%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=c9e254ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"f024b3eaa5b70cb64fc176e661e91e4839faeeb2","tid":1482234,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"大家明唔明白 818 星期日維園集會要full gear上陣點解 ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作用就係好似 警察開記者會咁， 啲記者全部full gear上陣。<br />\n<br />\n這就是表態，反映警察會對合法集會或普通平民射催淚彈， 用棍打， 射胡椒球。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家聽日全部要 full gear上陣, 和理非都要。<br />\n<br />\n豬嘴（口罩）, 長遮， 泳鏡， 有頭盔既就帶埋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多本地傳媒同外國傳媒影住架， 效果非同小可。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家明唔明白 ？"},{"pid":"92f2cdb92d973d460a3b365cd7dbca0c41926a00","tid":1482234,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818 塞爆維園<br />\n<br />\n但其實大家<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喺連登同溫層推無用</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n推就出街推<br />\n<br />\n依度要知嘅全部都知</span></span>"},{"pid":"72abc9e365ccb3fe477bb4fe58d7b1a1b8fb428b","tid":1482234,"uid":24224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"